{"type": "article", "id": 15356, "title": "关于二次元，有 21 个误解常常发生 | 每天还有一个 List", "description": "情况很严重。如果你不看标题就看正文，情况会更严重。", "date": "2015-10-02T08:39:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6723, "name": "二次元"}, {"id": 16437, "name": "误解向"}], "category": 3, "author": 57300, "comment_count": 81, "praise_count": 139, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133506PQukWRbADJU5OVv3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t1. <span> </span>二次元就是很二的意思。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021334544S9bJdV52ER0GHpz.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75076923\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t2.  二次元产业？一定是很容易赚（<span>Pian</span>）钱的生意。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133455Ssm2eUKFfbt89cpo.gif\" width=\"450\" height=\"253\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56222222\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t3.  喜欢二次元的人都是为了逃避现实。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133456rPRCQAVpYoBnhDIw.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"271\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.542\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t4.  二次元的东西全是日本来的。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133457DzCxNdFb2rajUA4n.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"736\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t5.  日本人都是二次元爱好者。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133457yaGi9ZIQWrcjzUSh.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"697\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t6.  二次元没有内涵。幼稚。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133458e0Njkw34soB7u6pG.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t7.  喜欢二次元的都是学生。而且很多小学生。<span></span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133458hV0OCKAN2jzi5Z6q.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t8.  二次元就是宅。不出门。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133459N20ATdaOoPskCuzb.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t9. <span> </span>喜欢二次元的男人都找不到女朋友。要么就找男朋友。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133500BL3ZyhVfFPOlbM4o.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t10. <span> </span>同人就是小黄书。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133500qBmCDjQTMHh78t5z.jpg\" width=\"675\" height=\"476\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t11.  萝莉控和正太控是恋童癖吧？\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133501Sms7gFMeJvBZH5lL.jpg\" width=\"704\" height=\"396\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t12.  二次元里的女主人公要么大胸，要么就是萌。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133501jNa1e8rK9HythOR0.gif\" width=\"420\" height=\"237\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56428571\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t13.<span>  </span>喜欢二次元的人也不会真在这上面花钱。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133502nMcgCtv2TQxOdm5S.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"246\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.492\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t14.  弄坏了它你至于这么生气？不就是碰坏了个玩具吗？手办？什么叫手办？\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021335021YLFH9Smd52lCiuE.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.14285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t15. <span> </span>玩<span> </span>Cosplay<span> </span>的人很多都是异装癖。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133503A3TvbwFYB0GcEfmO.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"694\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t16.  我家孩子喜欢画画，我觉得他是个二次元爱好者。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133504Om1WyoZ3HqCvxULM.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"363\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.726\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t17.  A 站 B 站应该是用来学英文的。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133504mfHLYTpNgIGxur5b.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"215\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t18.  鬼畜视频就是恐怖片。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133504m5EKUnR1xTItVpOi.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t19.<span><strong>  </strong></span><strong>我听见你刚刚问别人要</strong> av <strong>号了，嘿嘿。</strong> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133505UlrYbqHe59GBjatE.jpg\" width=\"719\" height=\"603\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83866481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t20.<span>  </span>中国的二次元爱好者<span> = </span>日本的御宅族。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133505WSJClQPT8ynI3w09.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t21.  中国最成功的二次元是《喜羊羊》和《熊出没》。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021335066VXNc1ja0fb25khg.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}